<div class="container">
  <div class="box">
    <img src="http://mishalandsamuel.com/logo.png">
    <p>A party updated their RSVP status! Here's a summary of the party's current information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>ID:</strong> <%= @party.id %></li>
      <li><strong>Code:</strong> <%= @party.code %></li>
      <li><strong>Guests:</strong></li>
      <ul>
        <% @party.guests.order("id ASC").find_each do |guest| %>
          <li><strong><%= guest.name %><% if guest.email.present? %> (<a href="mailto:<%= guest.email %>"><%= guest.email %></a>)<% end %></strong> - <%= guest.response.gsub("_", " ").titleize %><% if guest.attending? %> (<%= guest.meal.name %>)<% end %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <p>If you want a copy of the master CSV, just let me know!</p>
    <p class="closing">
      <span>Thanks,</span>
      <br>
      <span>Robin</span>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="copyright">&copy; 2015 Mishal &amp; Samuel</div>
</div>
